Closing the Hardware Target
You can close a hardware target by right-clicking on the hardware target in the Hardware window and selecting Close Target from the pop-up menu. You can also close the hardware target using a Tcl command. For instance, to close the xilinx\_platformusb/USB21 target on the local host server, use the following Tcl comm...
close_hw_target {localhost/xilinx_tcf/Digilent/210203339395A}
